### 2. React Components for Tools Tab

#### A. ToolTable Component
**File:** `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain-v1/lahore-v1/app/src/client/components/tool-registry/ToolTable.tsx`

**Key Types:**
```typescript
export type ToolListItem = {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  toolkit: string;
  description: string;
  risk_level: string;
  status: string;
  grant_count: number;
  governance_count: number;
  provider_name: string;
  created_at: string;
};

export type ToolTableFilters = {
  searchText: string;
  status?: string;
  riskLevel?: string;
};
```

**Key Functions (Pure View Model):**
- `deriveRiskBadge(riskLevel)` - Maps risk levels to badge styles (low/medium/high/critical)
- `deriveStatusBadge(status)` - Maps status (active/disabled) to badge styles
- `deriveProvenanceBadge(providerName)` - Shows tool source (manual or provider name)
- `filterTools(tools, filters)` - Filters by search, status, risk level
- `groupToolsByToolkit(tools)` - Groups tools by toolkit property
- `deriveToolTableViewModel(input)` - Derives complete UI state

**Component Rendering:**
- Groups tools by toolkit in collapsible sections
- Each group shows: Name, Description (truncated at 100 chars), Risk badge, Status badge, Grant count, Governance count, Source badge
- Shield emoji (🛡) indicates governed tools
- Clicking a row expands `ToolDetailPanel` for full details
- Supports filtering by search text, status, risk level

**Props:**
```typescript
type ToolTableProps = {
  tools: ToolListItem[];
  filters: ToolTableFilters;
};
```

